      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ISOLATION (1) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into second last time out (17.66) over 300m at Taree Super Track. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. SAVVY LAD (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 22.72 beating Rattlin' Magic. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Likely to be in the finish. DRINK ROSE (7) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when third (22.63) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Can feature again. HARADA'S LASS (5) will give backers a sight.",
